Russia May Link Gas Extraction Tax to World Prices, RIA Reports

-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 
2011-10-11T10:06:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/russia-may-link-gas-extraction-tax-to-world-prices-ria-reports.html
Russia may link the rate at which it
taxes natural-gas extraction to world prices for the fuel from
2013, RIA Novosti reported, citing Deputy Finance Minister
Sergei Shatalov.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow at 
 sbierman1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
